CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of nine men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence signing document, gathered around oval table in the Office of the Mayor in the City County Building
